ng the narrow cobbled streets enjoying a honey-soaked cake from one of the many cake shops or take in the restorative spa waters at Caldas de Monchique. ","url":"/poi/algarve/monchique-mountains","category":"Activities"},{"code":"FAO5050","title":"Praia de Vale do Lobo","images":{"thumbnail":"/-/media/fao_vale_de_lobo_golf_courses_636247404_getty_rgb-136-dpi-for-web.jpg","heroImage":"/-/media/fao_vale_de_lobo_golf_courses_636247404_getty_rgb-136-dpi-for-web.jpg"},"location":{"description":"Algarve, Portugal","latitude":37.04789,"longitude":-8.064724},"summary":"Backed by red-tinged cliffs and carpeted in golden sand, Praia de Vale do Lobo is a real stunner. ","url":"/poi/algarve/praia-de-vale-do-lobo","category":"Beaches"},{"code":"FAO5050","title":"Praia do Ancao","images":{"thumbnail":"/-/media/fao_generic_beach_1213510191_getty_rgb-136-dpi-for-web.jpg","heroImage":"/-/media/fao_generic_beach_1213510191_getty_rgb-136-dpi-for-web.jpg"},"location":{"description":"Algarve, Portugal","latitude":37.03276,"longitude":-8.038634},"summary":"Part of Ria Formosa Natural Park, Praia do Ancao is a long sandy beach backed by sand dunes and pine trees. ","url":"/poi/algarve/praia-do-ancao","category":"Beaches"},{"code":"FAO5050","title":"Praia do Garrao","images":{"thumbnail":"/-/media/fao_praia_de_garrao_nascente_980105990_getty_rgb-136-dpi-for-web.jpg","heroImage":"/-/media/fao_praia_de_garrao_nascente_980105990_getty_rgb-136-dpi-for-web.jpg"},"location":{"description":"Algarve, Portugal","latitude":37.039608,"longitude":-8.050372},"summary":"Swit swoo, Praia do Garrao is real beauty! ","url":"/poi/algarve/praia-do-garrao","category":"Beaches"},{"code":"","title":"Praia do Tonel","images":{"thumbnail":"/-/media/destination guide/portugal/algarve/gettyimages-175200196.jpg","heroImage":"/-/media/destination guide/portugal/algarve/gettyimages-175200196.jpg"},"location":{"description":"Algarve, Portugal","latitude":37.0060158,"longitude":-8.947801},"summary":"This sweep of golden